<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!DOCTYPE topic  PUBLIC '-//OASIS//DTD DITA Topic//EN'  'topic.dtd'><topic id="GUID_F1A181B0-C15C-4A43-8AF1-DB2DF91481DE"><title>ESD Diode Selection</title><body><section id="SECTION_ECBD5BE9-C40F-4BCF-B54D-3CBBF6D8C74B"><p>ESD diode selection recommendations below only apply to interfaces with:</p><ul><li><p>Hotplug input/output port application (external ports that exposed to end user)</p></li><li><p>Direct connection between SOC and connector (Eg, without redriver / retimer in between)</p></li></ul><p>For interfaces that require retimer:</p><ul><li><p>Intel retimer: Please refer to Thunderbolt retimer or controller documentation for more details, document number can be found in PDG chapter “EMC/RF Reference Documents”.</p></li><li><p>Third party retimer: Customer may contact vendor for necessary ESD protection.</p></li></ul><p>For further ESD design optimization, customers may refer to Chapter “System Efficient ESD Design (SEED)” for more details.</p><table id="TABLE_ECBD5BE9-C40F-4BCF-B54D-3CBBF6D8C74B_1" scale="60"><title>Discrete ESD Protection Diode Selection Guidelines</title><tgroup cols="6"><thead><row valign="top"><entry outputclass="rotate90">Interface </entry><entry outputclass="rotate90">Data Rate </entry><entry outputclass="rotate90">ESD Diode Placement </entry><entry outputclass="rotate90">ESD Diode Shunt Capacitance </entry><entry outputclass="rotate90">ESD Diode Rdyn </entry><entry outputclass="rotate90">ESD Diode Reverse Working Voltage </entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry><p>HDMI 2.1 Direct Connect Rate ≤ 6 Gbps (Data)   </p></entry><entry><p>≤ 6 Gbps </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 25 mm routing length from connector </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.4 pF </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.5 Ohm </p></entry><entry><p>4.0 V </p></entry></row><row><entry><p>HDMI 2.1 Direct Connect Rate &gt; 6Gbps (Data)</p></entry><entry><p>&gt; 6 Gbps </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 25 mm routing length from connector </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.4 pF </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.5 Ohm </p></entry><entry><p>4.0 V </p></entry></row><row><entry><p>HDMI connector HPD/DDC pins </p></entry><entry><p>  </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 25 mm routing length from connector </p></entry><entry><p>  </p></entry><entry><p>  </p></entry><entry><p>5.0 V </p></entry></row><row><entry><p>USB3.2 Gen1/2 Type A</p></entry><entry><p>≤10 Gbps </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 25 mm routing length from connector </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.35 pF </p></entry><entry><p>&lt; 0.5 Ohm </p></entry><entry><p>3.3 V </p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></body></topic>